			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Mixcloud has attracted content from world leading DJs, festivals and radio stations - from Carl Cox, Moby and Above &amp; Beyond to the Brooklyn Radio, Insomniac and Radiolab. The company has also worked with some of the world&#39;s largest brands and advertisers, including Nike, BlackBerry, Diesel, Red Bull, Smirnoff and Reebok. We are looking for a Brand Partnerships expert to help grow this area of the business.</p>
<p>
<br />
Role:</p>
<ul>
<li>
The focus of this role is to develop new business for Mixcloud from leading brands and agencies.</li>
<li>
There will also be some day to day account management of key accounts.</li>
<li>
Managing contact databases, target lists and the sales funnel.</li>
<li>
The role may also require some more general business development, since we are a small team and we require flexibility and a willingness to pitch in with everything.</li>
</ul>
<p>
You are:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Knowledgeable about trends and dynamics in social media, online advertising, content marketing and music, and a strong ability to communicate this to clients and prospective clients.</li>
<li>
Have a thorough understanding of the Mixcloud concept and it&#39;s benefit to brands.</li>
<li>
More than 3 years experience working in a very relevant role within the media, sales or marketing industry.</li>
<li>
A great networker and relationship builder, with an already strong and relevant list of contacts to bring to the role.</li>
<li>
Very well organised, motivated, independent and a quick learner.</li>
<li>
Persuasive and persistent!</li>
<li>
Excellent written and verbal communication skills.</li>
</ul>
<p>
How to apply:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Cover email including a link to your Linkedin profile (we do not accept CVs as attachments)</li>
<li>
Please include answers to the following questions:
<ul>
<li>
How strong and relevant is your network to Mixcloud and how you will leverage this to generate business for Mixcloud as quickly as possible.</li>
<li>
What experience do you have of pitching and generating new business?</li>
<li>
How effective are you at client management and communication? Please outline a positive example to demonstrate.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
